      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. can you make it a bit more descriptive about the actual people he's seeing and encountering? like, how they look or how their society seems to him compared to europe. make it feel more visceral—mentioning how they lack the proper discipline or refinement that we have, to really drive home that sense of them being \"uncivilized.\"",
